# Swim Intervals [Pool Swimming]

- warmup 200m @Z1
- 4x:
  - swim 100m @Z4
  - recover 50m @Z1
- cooldown 200m @Z1

# Rowing Warmup [Rowing]

- row 500m @Z1
- 3x:
  - row 250m @Z4
  - recover 250m @Z1
- row 100yd @Z2

# Bike Tempo [Cycling]

- warmup 10min @Z1
- bike 30min @85% of FTP
- cooldown 10min @Z1

# Brick Run [Running]

- run 3mi @7:00/mi
- cooldown 1mi @Z1

> Transition quickly from bike to run — simulate race day.
